stories: What is going on with our struggling facilities that care for the mentally challenged and those with Alzheimer's who have other medical issues? St. Mary's in Grand Junction just discharged a friend who broke a hip and has Alzheimer's, without rehabilitation for the hip and no available beds for Alzheimer's patients! Ludicrous! The authorities closed the facility to accommodate "challenged" residents here last year and relocated them to Denver. Ridiculous! Our healthcare system is without compassion and based on the bottom line! The worst part is drug addicts and emergency room managers can get care, but we treat those with health issues as seniors like shit! Sad state of affairs! Shame on healthcare and those who do not fight for dignity in end-of-life care! Shameful! Politicians should be ashamed for not supporting a bill that cares for these people!

What is happening with our struggling facilities that take care of the mentally challenged and those with Alzheimer's who have other medical issues? St. Mary's in Grand Junction just released a friend who broke a hip and has Alzheimer's, without rehabilitation for the hip and no available beds for Alzheimer's patients! Unbelievable! The authorities closed the facility to accommodate "challenged" residents here last year and moved them to Denver. Ridiculous! Our healthcare system is without compassion and based on the bottom line! The worst part is drug addicts and emergency room managers can get care, but we treat those with health issues as seniors like garbage! A sad state of affairs! Shame on healthcare and those who do not fight for dignity in end-of-life care! Shameful! Politicians should be ashamed for not supporting a bill that cares for these people!
